videos.description: Mohamed Bamba gets inside the paint and extends his arms up to deny Ole Miss' layup attempt in the first half.
videos.headline: Mo Bamba reaches high to hold off Ole Miss

videos.description: Dylan Osetkowski intercepts the ball and explodes to the rim for a one-handed dunk in the first half against Ole Miss.
videos.headline: Osetkowski steals and slams for Longhorns

videos.description: Mo Bamba drills a 3-pointer from the top of the key to extend the Longhorns' lead to 43-32 against Ole Miss late in the first half.
videos.headline: Mo Bamba shows off from behind the arc

videos.description: Mo Bamba receives the lob from Matt Coleman and attacks the rim with a two-handed slam in the second half.
videos.headline: Mo Bamba soars for alley-oop slam

videos.description: Dylan Osetkowski finds Mo Bamba and he finishes with another monster two-handed jam for the Longhorns.
videos.headline: Osetkowski feeds Bamba for the flush

videos.description: Mo Bamba stretches out to block Ole Miss' shot attempt in the second half.
videos.headline: Ole Miss can't get past Bamba

videos.description: Mo Bamba grabs Jase Febres' miss and turns around to destroy the rim with a vicious one-handed slam in the second half.
videos.headline: Bamba keeps it alive and throws down the hammer

videos.description: Dave Pasch and Robbie Hummel applaud Mo Bamba's performance against Ole Miss on Saturday where the true freshman got his 10th career double-double with 25 points and 15 rebounds.
videos.headline: Bamba scores career-high 25 in victory over Ole Miss
